      "text": "「人気絶頂のサニーピースが伝説のアイドル長瀬麻奈の\n曲をカバーすることにファンの期待が高まっている」",
      "startTime": 135.7333788395,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "……何も問題ないと思うが",
      "startTime": 140.8395197344,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_01-skr014.m4a",
      "text": "問題はこの後です！\n「疑問なのは、サニピと月ストが合同で歌うことだ」",
      "startTime": 145.9000455062,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_01-skr015.m4a",
      "text": "「両グループで別々に歌うことも出来たのに\nなぜわざわざ人気に差がある二組を組ませたのか」",
      "startTime": 154.9000414372,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_01-skr016.m4a",
      "text": "「関係者の話では、人気に翳りが見えてきた月ストへの\nてこ入れとして、BIG4のサニピと組ませたと――」",
      "startTime": 164.7333676498,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_01-skr017.m4a",
      "text": "なんなんですか！　この自称関係者を\n連れて来て下さい！　私が直接文句を言います！",
      "startTime": 172.5666989487,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_01-skr018.m4a",
      "text": "月ストを馬鹿にする人は私が許しませんっ！",
      "startTime": 177.0223436784,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_01-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "確かにこれは言い過ぎだ\nすぐに三枝さんに話して出版社に伝えておくよ",
      "startTime": 183.8178228648,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_01-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "それにしても月ストのために怒るなんてさくららしいな\nさくら自身もいろいろ言われているのに……",
      "startTime": 192.0844803761,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_01-skr019.m4a",
      "text": "え？　いろいろってなんですか？",
